OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBlustery, cloudy, and damp with
OL,6,Flight rain and drizzly outbreaks
OL,7,Fpossible for much of the day. Low
OL,8,Fcloud and misty conditions likely
OL,9,Facross high ground and in coastal
OL,10,Fareas. Temperatures slightly above
OL,11,Faverage.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy well into
OL,14,Fthe evening, perhaps with a little
OL,15,Flight drizzle in places. Skies
OL,16,Fclearing for a time from the north
OL,17,Fbefore more cloud arrives towards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
