OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy start on Saturday,
OL,6,Fwith thicker cloud soon arriving with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain. Turning
OL,8,Fincreasingly windy as Storm Dave
OL,9,Farrives with risk of coastal gales
OL,10,Fdeveloping.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,13,Fbut blustery on Easter Sunday, with
OL,14,Fscattered showers. Winds easing
OL,15,Fleaving a drier, brighter, and warmer
OL,16,FEaster Monday. Settled initially on
OL,17,FTuesday, but clouding over with rain
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
